title: Encyclopedia of Smart Materials [Vols 1 and 2]
description:
The Encyclopedia of Smart Materials (ESM) contains the
writings, thoughts, and work of many of the world?s foremost
people (scientists, educators, chemists, engineers,
laboratory and innovative practitioners) who work in the
field of smart materials. The authors discuss theory, fundamentals,
fabrication, processing, application, applications
and uses of these very special, and in some instances rare,
materials.
